What are the dress code requirements for the final exams at UTM?
answer: According to the FKE Final Examination Briefing to all invigilators, you are strongly advised to follow the UTM dress code for all your final exam papers to ensure that you do not face any problem entering the exam hall. Other than the attire, you shall have: 1. No ear piercing/ear rings for boys, 2. To wear proper shoes unless the hall requires you to take off shoes, 3. No dyed hair, 4. Make sure your hair is neat.
